# Code Review Delegation

Delegating comprehensive code review to the **guide-review** agent.

The review agent will:
- Read the `.guide` file to understand the current issue context
- Load code review guidelines from the "code-review" collection
- Analyze recent changes in the context of the current issue
- Create or update the review artifact in `.todo/` directory

